    </font> <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">&#147;Ma
    iau, a tara na turagu, pa ina pait valar pa ia ba ina tata ta vavat da tadav
    diat dia tulungen, vada ta diat ika dia palapaka, da ta diat dia kuramana
    tai Kristo.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Iau tar tabar avat
    ma ra polo na u, vakir ma ra dekdek na magit;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
    </span>tago pa ava ga patuan upi ia;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>maia,
    ma gori pa ava patuan boko upi ia;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>tago
