"><b style><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span><font size="4">GOD I TAR TABAR DAT MA RA NILAUN NINA I OT MA I BUKA LEKE.</font></b></span></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div>
<p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">Iesu
i biti, &#147;Iau ga vut upi diat a vatur vake ra nilaun, a nilaun i buka ma ra
boina.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Ioanes
10:10)</font></b></span></p>
<span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">&#147;Iau
ra vain ma avat a lavur ingarigu;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>nina
i ki tagu, ma iau bula, iau ki tana, na manga vuai;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>tago ona da ki varbaiai, pa avat a pait valar pa ta magit.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Ioanes 15:5)</font></b></span>
<p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">&#147;Ma
ra vuai ra Tulungen ia ra varmari, a gugu, a malmal, a kini na varvamadudur, a
bala varmari, a bo na mangamangana, a dovotina, a madu na bala, a mangamangana
vinvini, ma pa ta varkurai na tur bat ure ra dari.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Galatia 5:22-23)</font></b></span>
<p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">&#147;Ma
avat, avat a vatur vake ra dekdek boko, ba ra Takodo na Tulungen na irop taun
avat;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>ma avat a varveai tagu aro
Ierusalem, ma ta ra gunagunan par Iudaia ma Samaria, ma tuk ta ra mutuai na
langlangun na rakaradan a gunagunan.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Apostolo 1:8)</font></b></span> <br>
        <br>
<span style="
;mso-fareast-;
"><b>NINA
I BUKA MA RA TULUNGEN.</b><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Nina i
buka ma ra Tulungen, i nur tar ra Takodo na Tulungen upi na kure kana nilaun.</span><br>
<div align="center">
  <center>
    <table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="4">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt"><b>A
          Takodo na Tulungen i tul tar ra dekdek pirana:</b></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">Upi
          na ve ra umana enana ure Kristo<br>
          Upi na araring<br>
          Upi na matoto ta ra tinata kai God<br>
          Upi na nurnur tai God<br>
          </span><span style=";

">Upi na torom tai God</span></p>
        </td>
        <td width="23%" valign="middle" align="center">
        <img border="0" src="images/kua2-2.gif" width="190" height="191"></td>
        <td valign="middle">
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt"><b>A
          Takodo na Tulungen i&nbsp;tabar ia ma:</b></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">&nbsp;Ra
          Varmari&nbsp;<br>
          Ra Gugu<br>
          Ra Malmal<br>
          Ra Kini Varvamadudur<br>
          Ra Bala Varmari<br>
          Ra Bo na Mangamangana<br>
          </span><span style=";

">Ra Dovotina</span></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </center>
</div>
</center>

<p align="left"><br>
<span style=".0pt">Ba i tavua vanavana
kaum nurnur tai God ure ra lavur magit parika, go ra lavur magit diat a vana
rikai vanavana ta kaum nilaun.<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Ona u turpa ia ka upi una nunure ra papalum kai ra Takodo na
Tulungen, koko una ligur ona pa u tadav vauvue go ra lavur magit.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Ta ra turpaina, vakir una da ra tutana nina i ga nurnur tai God mangoro na
kilakilala.</span> 
    </p>

<p align="left">
<span style=".0pt">Ava ra vuna mangoro na
te Kristo vakir dia vatur vake go ra bo na nilaun, nina i buka leke ma i lia?</span>
    </p>
<center>

    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><span style=" 10.0pt;          ;  normal"><b style=" normal;  10.0pt;          "><font size="6">2.</font></b></span><span style=";

"><b style=" normal; font-size: 12.0pt;  10.0pt;          ">&nbsp;
          </b><b style><font size="4">A UMANA TE KRISTO PA KIAT A
          VATUR VAKE RA BO NA NILAUN NINA I BUKA LEKE MA I LIA, ONA DIA NUKNUK URE
          DIAT IAT IKA.</font></b></span></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div><p align="left"><span style=".0pt">A
tutana nina i nuk pa ia iat ika, i nurnur tana iat upi na laun da ra te Kristo:</span> </p>
</center>

<p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(a)<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Kan pa ta tikai i tar ve vakapa ure ra varmari kai God ma ra dekdekina,
ma ba God i pun vue kada varpiam.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Ba
kan i tar valubane.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Rom
5:8-10;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Ebraio 10:1-25;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>1
Ioanes 1:1-10;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>1 Ioanes 2:1-2;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>2 Petero 1:9;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Apostolo 1:8).</font></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(b)<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Kana nilaun i tutua ma i kuba mulai.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(c)<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>I mainge upi na pait ra boina, ia kaka i mama pait valar pa ia.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(d)<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Pa i nurnur ta ra Takodo na Tulungen upi na vadekdek ia, upi na laun ma
ra nilaun tuna.</span></p>
<center>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">&nbsp;</span><span style=";

"><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(1 Korinto 3:1-3;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Rom 7:15-24;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Rom 8:7;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Galatia 5:16-18).</font></b></span></p>
    <p><br>
    <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
"><b>NINA
    I NUKNUK URE IA IAT IKA</b> &#150; Go ra umana magit dia vung vaarike ra te
    Kristo nina pa i ot kana nurnur tai God:</span> <br>
    </p>
<div align="center">
  <center>
    <table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="4">
      <tr>
        <td><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">Vakir
          i nunure ba ava ra Takodo na Tulungen na pait ia ure kana nilaun.</span><br>
          <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
"><br>
          Pa i nurnur tai God, ma pa i torom tana.</span><br>
          <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
"><br>
          Pa i mari God ma pa i mari ra umana&nbsp;</span><br>
 <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">enana.</span><br>
          <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
"><br>
          Vakir i mainge upi na vartovo ta ra Buk&nbsp;Tabu.</span></td>
        <td valign="middle" align="center">
        <img border="0" src="images/kua3-1.gif" width="190" height="191"></td>
        <td><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">I
          laun ta ra umana varkurai, ma vakir ta ra nurnur.<br>
          I laun ma ra bunurut, ma vakir ma ra varmari.<br>
          I dur ra umana nuknukina.<br>
          Ia ra tena varurai.<br>
          I ruva, tago i rara.<br>
          I ngarao ma i ligur.<br>
          I gire ke ra umana kaina magit ta ra lavur magit par&nbsp;ma
          ta ra tarai par.</span>
          <span style="
;mso-fareast-;
"><strong><br>
          </strong>
          I alalir vurvurbit, ma pa ta vunapai kana nilaun, ma&nbsp;pa i
          kapa ba i mainge ra ava.</span></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </center>
</div>
<p align="left"><br>
<span style=".0pt">(A tutana nina i pait
vatikene ra kaina, kan vakir ia ra dovot na te Kristo.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">1 Ioanes 2:3-5;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>1 Ioanes 3:6-9;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Epeso
5:5).</font></b></span> <br>
    <br>
<em><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">A
    vautuluna mamat na nuknuk i varve dat ure ra balbali.</span></em></p>
    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b style=" normal;  10.0pt;          "><span style=" 10.0pt;          ;  normal"><font size="6">3.</font></span></b><span style=";

"><b style><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span><font size="4">NILAUN, NINA I BUKA LEKE MA I LIA, PIRE DIAT DIA IESU I GA
          VAVALIMA BA NA TUL TAR RA DOVOT NA MULAOT UPI A TAKODO NA TULUNGEN NA
          KURE KADIA NILAUN.</font></b></span></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div>
</center>

    <p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">A
Tulungen i kure ta tutana ona Kristo, i laun tana ma ra dekdek i ra Takodo na
Tulungen <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Ioanes, a pakana 15).</font></b></span>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(A)<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Ona d ul tar iu upi u a te Kristo, a
Takodo na Tulungen i ruk ma i ki ta kaum nilaun par, pa na mutu <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Ioanes
1:12, Kolose 2:9-10;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Ioanes
14:16-17).</font></b>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt"><br>
</span><span style="
.0pt">A Takodo na Tulungen i ki ta ra lavur te Kristo
parika, ia kaka ta umana te Kristo pa dia mulaot upi a Takodo no Tulungen na
kure diat.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">(B)<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>A Takodo na Tulungen i tabar dat ma ra nilaun i buka leke<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Ioanes 7:37-39).</font></b></span>
    </p>
<p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">(C)<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>A Takodo na Tulungen i ga vut upi na vaki Kristo ta ra kini na lualua<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Ioanes 16:1-15)</font></b>.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Ona a Takodo na Tulungen i kure ta
tutana, nam ra tutana bula na vung Kristo ta ra kini na lualua ta kana nilaun.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
<p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">(D)<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>Ta kana mutuaina vartuluai, ba pa i ga tutua boko urama ra bala na bakut,
Kristo i ga vavalima ba na tul tar ra Takodo&nbsp;na
Tulungen pire dat, ma ba ra Takodo na Tulungen na vadekdek dat upi dat a varveai
tai Kristo<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Apostolo
1:1-9).</font></b></span>
    <p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">Io,
    ra Takodo na Tulungen na kure, ba vabuka, davatane ta tutana?</span></p>
<center>

    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b style=" normal;  10.0pt"><span style=" 10.0pt;  normal"><font size="6">4.</font></span></b><span style="
10.0pt"><b style><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;
          </span><font size="4">A TAKODO NA TULUNGEN I KURE DAT BA DA NURNUR.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>ONA DAMANA, DAT A KAIRANE RA NILAUN NINA I BUKA LEKE MA I LIA,
          BA KRISTO I GA VAVALIMA BA NA TUL TAR IA PIRE TIKATIKA NA TE KRISTO.</font></b></span></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div>
</center>

    <p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">A
Takodo na Tulungen i tale upi na kure kaum nilaun gori iat.</span>
<p align="left"><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">(A)<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>Ona u mainge damana <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Mattaio 5:6;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>Ioanes 7:37-39)</font></b></span>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(B)<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Ona u varvai kapa pire God ure
kaum lavur varpiam.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<span style="
.0pt">Una nurnur ma una pite pa God tago i tar re vue kaum
lavur varpiam&#151;diat nina u tar pait diat lua, diat nina u pait diat gori, ma
diat nina ba una pait ia boko&#151;tago Kristo i ga mat ure u<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Kolose 2:13-15; 1 Ioanes 1:1-10;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>1 Ioanes 2:1-3;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Ebraio 10:1-17).</font></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt">(C)<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Ta ra nurnur una matoto ba ra
Takodo na Tulungen i vabuka nilaun.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Ia
iat kaum lualua ma i kure u, ta go:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt"><span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b>1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">
</span>KANA VARTULUAI</b>&#151;Una buka ma ra Tulungen.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.5in"><span style="
.0pt">&#147;Ma koko avat a longlong ma ra mome vain, nina ba i
vuna ta ra lavur bilak na magit, avat a buka ma ra Tulungen.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Epeso 5:18).</font></b></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style=".0pt"><b>2.<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp; </span>KANA VAMADING</b>&#151;Ia na bali vatikene kada niaring, ona da
araring ma ra tinorom ta ra nuknukina.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.5in;text-indent:-.5in" align="left"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt;  10.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span><span style=";

">&#147;Ma go ia ra magit da rururung tana taday ia,
tago ba da lul ta magit da ra nuknukina, i vatorome dat;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span>ma ba da nunure ba i valongore dat ta ra magit par ba da lul ia, da
matoto bula ba da tar vatur vake nam da ga lul ia tana.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
</span><b><font color="#1C1CB0">(1 Ioanes 5:14-15).</font></b></span></p>
<p align="left"><span style=".0pt">Una vung vaarike
kaum nurnur ta ra niaring&#133;</span></p>
<center>

<center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><b style><span style=";

">A NGA NA NIARING MA RA NURNUR, UPI RA TAKODO NA
          TULUNGEN NA KURE U MA NA LUE RAP U.</span></b></p>
        <p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">A
        Takodo na Tulungen i kure dat ma i lue rap dat ona da nurnur uka.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>A dovot na niaring, ia tika na nga upi una vaarike kaum nurnur
        tana.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Dave, i tale upi una
        araring ma go ra niaring:</span> </p>
        <blockquote>
          <p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">&#147;Tamagu,
          a tena varmari, iau iba upi u.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Iau
          tar vala kure kaugu nilaun, ma damana iau tar piam vue u.<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Iau pite pa u tago u tar re vue kaugu lavur varpiam, tago
          Kristo i ga mat ure iau ta ra bolo.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Ma go iau lul upi Kristo na kure mule kaugu nilaun.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Una vabuka iau ma ra Takodo na Tulungen, vade u ga vartuluai
          upi avet a buka me.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Iau
          nurnur ba kaum vamading piragu i dovot, damana iau vatang boina piram
          go ta ra iang i Iesu Kristo a Natum.&#148;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">Dave
        u mainge upi ra Takodo na Tulungen na kure u?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>Ona u mainge damana, una araring ma una nurnur tai God gori iat.</span> </p>
        <hr>
          <p align="center"><b style><span style=".0pt">UNA
          NUNURE DAVATANE BA RA TAKODO NA TULUNGEN I KURE U?</span></b></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">Dave,
          u tar lul God upi na vabuka u ma ra Takodo na Tulungen?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Dave, u nunure ba ra Takodo na Tulungen i kure u ma i lue rap u
          gori?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>To ia i ga biti ba
          na dari?<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>God iat, ta kana
          tinata:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Ebraio 11:6;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Rom 14:22-23.</span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">I
          topa dat ba dat a nurnur ta ra lavur vamading ta ra tinata kai God, ma
          koko da nurnur ta ra umana kakairanai ta ra bala i dat.</span></p>
          <span style=";

">Kada kakairanai i pupukuai vatikai.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Ta umana pakana da kairane ba ra lavur magit dia boina, ma ona
          dia kaina vanavana da turpa ia upi dat a nunuk lalar.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>A te Kristo i laun ta ra nurnur;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>i nurnur tai God ma ta kana umana vamading, nina dia varogop
          vatikai ma pa dia pupukuai muka.<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>(Ioanes 14:21)</span><br>
          <p align="center"><img border="0" src="images/kautrcktr.gif" width="561" height="212"></p>
        <p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">Go
        ra trakta ma terela dir valarue go ra magit, ba ava ra vuna ba pa i topa
        dat upi dat a nurnur ta kada kakairanai.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>A trakta ia ra lavur dovot na vamading kai God, nina dia ki ta
        kana tinata.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>A terela nina
        di pakan tar ia ta ra trakta, ia kada nurnur tai God ma ta kana tinata.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>A kinakap, ia kada kakairanai.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>A kinakap pa i tale upi na maravut ra trakta ma ra terela.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>A trakta i tale upi na vanavana varkolono, ia kaka a terela pa i
        tale upi na al ra trakta.<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Damana kad nurnur i ki ta ra umana dovot na vamading kai God.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>Kada nurnur i pakan tar dat tai God.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>Da nurnur ta ra vamading, ma vakir ta kada kakairanai ure.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
        </span>Vakir da nurnur ta kada kakairanai.</span> </p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b style><span style=";

">A NGA URE RA KINI TA RA TULUNGEN</span></b></p>
        <p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">A
        kopono nga ba ra te Kristo na mur ia, upi a Tulungen na kure kana nilaun,
        ia ra nurnur:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>a nurnur tai
        God ma ta kana umana vamading.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Ona
        u nurnur vatikai:</span>
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in"><span style=".0pt">(A)<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Kaum nilaun na vung vaarike ra vuai ra
          Tulungen, ma na tavua vanavana <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Galatia
          5:22-23)</font></b>;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>ma
          kaum nilaun na pupukuai vanavana upi amur a varogop ma Kristo <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Rom
          12:2;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>2 Korinto 3:18).</font></b></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in"><span style=".0pt">(B)<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Kaum uman niaring ma kaum niluluk
          ta ra Buk Tabu diat a ngatngat piram, ma una kap ra bo na kukuraina
          tana.</span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
          </span>(C)<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
          </span>Una vatur vake ra dekdekina upi una varveai tana <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Apostolo
          1:8).</font></b></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in"><span style=".0pt">(D)<span style="mso-tab-count:
1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Una ki na vaninara upi una varubu ma ra
          umana kaina magit ta ra rakarakan a gunagunan <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(1
          Ioanes 2:15-17)</font></b>&#133;.ma ra umana kaina magit na palapaka <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(Galatia
          5:16-17)</font></b>&#133;.ma ma Satan <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(1 Petero
          5:7-9;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Epeso 6:10-13).</font></b></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-indent:-.5in"><span style=";

">(E)<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
          </span>Una vatur vake ra dekdek upi una vatang PATA ta ra lavur magit
          dia kaina <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(1 Korinto 10:13;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Pilipoi 4:13;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Epeso
          1:19-23;<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp; </span>Epeso 6:10;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>2
          Timoteo 1:7;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Rom 6:1-16).</font></b></span></p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b style><span style=";

">A VUVU NA TULUNGEN</span></b></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">Ta
          ra nurnur, i tale upi una nunure ba God i mari u ma ba i re vue kaum
          lavur varpiam, ta ra bungbung par.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Amur a varagur ma ra Luluai ma una kudar pirana.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Ta nam ra pakana bung ba u nunure ba ta magit ta kaum nilaun
          nina vakir a Luluai i gugu ure, una ve lulut ia.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Ma una vatang boina tuna pire God tago i tar re vue kaum lavur
          varpiam, tago lesu Kristo i ga mat ta ra bolo.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Una alube kana varmari ma kana punpun vuai upi kaum iat, ta ra
          nurnur, ma amur a ki varurung ma God ta ra bungbung vatikai.<span style="mso-spacerun:
yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">Ona
          u turpa ia upi u iat una kure mule kaum nilaun, go ia ra varpiam.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>I topa dat upi dat a vartovo upi dat a vuvu tar ra tulungen ta
          kada nilaun.</span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">A
          VUVU NA TULUNGEN i dari:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>da
          vuvu vue ra dur ma da vuvu tar ra gomgom.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Go na vadekdek u upi una vala kairane ba God i mari u ma ba i
          pun vue kaum lavur varpiam.</span></p>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><span style=".0pt">1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">
          </span>VU VUE&#151;una ve God ure kaum lavur varpiam&#151;koko una valar ia
          upi una ive ta, magit tana kan God ba kan u iat;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>ma namur una pite pa ia tago i tar re vue <b><font color="#1C1CB0">(1
          Ioanes 1:9 ma Ebraio 10:1-25)</font></b>.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>Ba da tar tata kapa ure kada lavur varpiam, i topa ia ba ra
          nuknuk i dat ma kada mangamangana diat a enana iat.</span></p>
          <span style=";

">2.<span style="mso-tab-count:1"> </span>KAP RA
          VUVU&#151;Una alube Kristo upi na kure kaum nilaun ta ra dekdek i ra
          Takodo na Tulungen.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Ta ra
          nurnur, una ma toto ba gori kure u ma i vadekdek u.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
          </span>go ia ra vartuluai nina i ki tai <b><font color="#1C1CB0">Epeso
          5:18</font></b>, ma ra vamading nina i ki tai <b><font color="#1C1CB0">1
          Ioanes 5:14-15.</font></b></span>
        <hr>
        <p><span style="
;mso-fareast-;
">ONA
        GO RA IK A BUK I TAR MARAVUT U, MA U TAR KAP RA BO NA TINATA TANA, I
        BOINA BA UNA TUL TAR IA PIRE TA TIKAI, BA UNA LUK IA PIRANA.</span> <br>
